nment, Predictions, Reviews|language=en|access-date=2019-12-24}}</ref>\n|-\n| Best Original Song\n| Kristen Anderson-Lopez & Robert Lopez (<small>for \"Into the Unknown\")</small>\n| {{nominated}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[NAACP Image Award]]s\n| [[51st NAACP Image Awards|February 22, 2020]]\n| Outstanding Character Voice-Over Performance\n| [[Sterling K. Brown]]\n| {{nom}}\n| align=center| <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/2020-naacp-image-award-winners-complete-list-updating-1276771|title=NAACP Image Awards: Lizzo Named Entertainer of the Year; 'Just Mercy,' 'Black-ish' Among Top Winners}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"4\"| [[Nickelodeon Kids' Choice Awards]]\n| rowspan=\"4\"| [[2020 Kids' Choice Awards|TBD]]\n| [[Kids' Choice Award for Favorite Animated Movie|Favorite Animated Movie]]\n| ''Frozen II''\n| {{pending}}\n|rowspan=\"4\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2020/02/avengers-end-game-leads-nickelodeons-kids-choice-awards-nominations-billie-eilish-taylor-swift-chance-the-rapper-full-list-1202859259/|title=Nickelodeon's Kids' Choice Awards Nominations: 'Avengers: Endgame' Leads \u2013 Deadline|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Denise|last=Petski|date=February 13, 2020|accessdate=February 13, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| Favorite Male Voice from an Animated Movie \n| Josh Gad\n| {{pending}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| Favorite Female Voice from an Animated Movie \n| Kristen Bell\n| {{pending}}\n|-\n| Idina Menzel\n| {{pending}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Producers Guild of America Award]]s\n| [[Producers Guild of America Awards 2019|January 18, 2020]]\n| [[Producers Guild of America Award for Best Animated Motion Picture|Outstanding Producer of Animated Theatrical Motion Pictures]]\n| ''Frozen II''\n| {{nominated}}\n| align=center| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2020/film/news/pga-awards-winners-2020-1203471639/|title=PGA Awards Winners: Complete List|website=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|first=Adam|