ward\n!Category \n!Nominated work\n!Result\n|-\n|1980\n|[[Drama Desk Award]] \n|[[Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Actor in a Play|Outstanding Actor in a Play]]\n|''[[The Suicide (play)|The Suicide]]''\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|1983\n|[[Laurence Olivier Award]]\n|[[Laurence Olivier Award for Actor of the Year in a Revival|Best Actor in a Revival]]\n|''[[Cyrano de Bergerac (play)|Cyrano de Bergerac]]''\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|1983\n|[[Critics' Circle Theatre Awards]]\n|[[Critics' Circle Theatre Awards#Best Actor|Best Actor]]\n|''[[Cyrano de Bergerac (play)|Cyrano de Bergerac]]'' <br/>''[[Much Ado About Nothing]]''\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|1983\n|[[Evening Standard Awards]] \n|[[Evening Standard Awards|Best Actor]]\n|''[[Much Ado About Nothing]]''\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|1984\n|[[Tony Award]]\n|[[Tony Award for Best Actor in a Play|Best Actor in a Play]]\n|''[[Much Ado About Nothing]]''\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|1985\n|[[Drama Desk Award]]\n|[[Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Actor in a Play|Outstanding Actor in a Play]]\n|''[[Much Ado About Nothing]]'' <br/>''[[Cyrano de Bergerac (play)|Cyrano de Bergerac]]'' \n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|1986\n|[[Laurence Olivier Award]]\n|[[Laurence Olivier Award for Best Actor|Best Actor]]\n|rowspan=3|''[[Breaking the Code]]''\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|1988\n|[[Drama Desk Award]]\n|[[Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Actor in a Play|Outstanding Actor in a Play]]\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|1988\n|[[Tony Award]]\n|[[Tony Award for Best Actor in a Play|Best Actor in a Play]]\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|2009\n|[[Laurence Olivier Award]]\n|[[Laurence Olivier Award for Best Actor|Best Actor]]\n|''[[Twelfth Night]]''\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|}\n\n;Television\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!Year\n!Award\n!Category \n!Nominated work\n!Result\n|-\n|1976\n|[[British Academy Television Award]]\n|[[British Academy Television Award for Best Actor|Best Actor]]\n|''[[I, Claudius (TV series)|I, Claudius]]''\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|1977\n|[[British Academy Television Award]]\n|[[British Academy Television Award for Best Actor|Best Actor]]\n|''Philby, Bu