ont-size:80%\" | \"\u2014\" denotes a recording that did not chart or was not released in that territory.\n|}\n\n==Accolades==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|+Music program award\n! width=\"200\"|Program\n! width=\"140\"|Date\n! {{abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n| ''[[M Countdown]]'' ([[Mnet (TV channel)|Mnet]])\n| April 16, 2020\n| <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mydaily.co.kr/new_yk/html/read.php?newsid=202004161801178159&ext=na|script-title=ko:[\uc885\ud569] '\uc5e0\uce74' (\uc5ec\uc790)\uc544\uc774\ub4e4, 1\uc704 \"\ud32c\ub4e4\uc5d0\uac8c \ub2f9\ub2f9\ud55c \uc544\ud2f0\uc2a4\ud2b8 \ub418\uaca0\ub2e4\"|publisher=MyDaily|date=April 16, 2020}}</ref>\n|}\n\n{|| width=\"75%\" class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|+Awards and nominations\n|-\n! Year\n! Award-Giving Body\n! Category\n!Nominated work\n! Result\n! Ref\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[34th Golden Disc Awards|2020]]\n| [[Golden Disc Awards]]\n| Best Female Performance Award\n| rowspan=\"2\" | \"Lion\"\n| {{won}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://pop.heraldcorp.com/view.php?ud=202001051655489275771_1|script-title=ko:[2020 \uace8\ub4e0\ub514\uc2a4\ud06c]\uc544\uc2a4\ud2b8\ub85c\u00b7(\uc5ec\uc790)\uc544\uc774\ub4e4, \ubca0\uc2a4\ud2b8\ud37c\ud3ec\uba3c\uc2a4\uc0c1 \"\uc0c8\ud574 \ucd9c\ubc1c\ubd80\ud130 \uac10\uc0ac\"|date=January 5, 2020|work=HeraldPop|language=ko}}</ref> \n|-\n| [[Korean Music Awards]]\n|align=\"center\"|Best Pop Song\n|{{nom}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|url= https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/now/article/311/0001102778|title= \ubc29\ud0c4\uc18c\ub144\ub2e8\ubd80\ud130 \uc545\ubba4\uae4c\uc9c0\u2026\u2018\ud55c\ub300\uc74c\u2019 \uc62c\ud574 \uc2dc\uc0c1\uc2dd \ud6c4\ubcf4 \ubc1c\ud45c [\ud604\uc7a5]|work=Naver|publisher=XSportsNews|date=January 22, 2020|language=ko}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Release history==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n! Region\n! Date\n! Format\n! Distributor\n! {{abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| South Korea\n| rowspan=\"3\" | April